# REQUIREMENTS
We need to analyze key indicators for our pizza sales data to gain insights into our business performance. Specifically, we want to calculate the following metrics:
Total Revinew
Average Order Value
Total Pizzas Sold
Total Oders
Average Pizza Per Order
Hourly Trends for total pizzas sold
Weekly trends for total pizzas sold
Percentage of pizza sold by category
Percentage of pizza sold by size
Total pizza sold by category
Top 5 best seller by Revenew, Total quantity and total orders
Bottom 5 best seller by Revenew, Total quantity and total orders
